TEXT.TITLE: KEY TRONIC <KTCC> GETS NEW BUSINESS
TEXT.BODY: Key Tronic corp said it has received contracts to provide seven original equipment manufacturers with which it has not done business recently with over 300,000 computer keyboards for delivery within the next 12 months. The company said "The new contracts represent an annual increase of approximately 25 pct in unit volume over last year." Reuter
